data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom house is now available for sale.  As you step inside, you'll notice the laminate flooring that runs throughout the entire house, creating a modern look. The HVAC system was upgraded in 2022, ensuring year-round comfort and energy efficiency. The roof was also replaced in the same year, providing peace of mind for years to come. Additionally, the plumbing and gas lines were updated in 2023, further adding to the overall value of this home.  With double-pane windows and new siding, this property offers improved insulation and a fresh exterior appearance. The almost complete remodeling showcases the care and attention to detail put into this house.  Conveniently located near the Medical Center, this home offers easy access to healthcare facilities, shopping centers, and restaurants. The surrounding area has seen significant growth potential, making it an attractive investment opportunity. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your own.
